Description: A toolkit for visualising data used in, and produced by, stock assessment models. 
    Raw model outputs from specific stock assessment models (so far Stock Synthesis and DDUST) can 
    be transformed into report-ready graphics, tables and values, and plugged directly into a report
    template. Raw data can also be visualised using individual functions or through comprehensive 
    investigation tools. 
